    <h1>Marketing Strategy</h1>
    <p class="description">A company's long-term game plan for reaching its target audience, communicating its value, and driving profitable customer action — determining which channels, audiences, and messages to prioritize.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
