              <tr><td><strong>Social Media</strong></td><td>Brand building, community</td><td>3–12 months</td><td>Engagement, reach</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Account-Based Marketing</strong></td><td>Enterprise B2B, large deals</td><td>3–9 months</td><td>Pipeline from target accounts</td></tr>
